    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Urocaridella arabianensis n. sp., a new Palaemonid shrimp (Crustacea, Decapoda Palaemonidae) from Lakshadweep Islands, India with taxonomic comparison on the genus Urocaridella Borradaile, 1915" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954095>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954097>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954099>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954101>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954103>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954105>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954107>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954109> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954095>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Urocaridella arabianensis n. sp. Holotype, Female (13 mm): lateral view of carapace (A); close view of distal teeth of rostrum (B); eye (C); Antennal scaphocerite (D); Antennular peduncle (E); mandible (F); maxillula (G); Maxilla (H); Maxilliped I (I); Maxilliped II (J); Maxilliped III (K)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954095/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954097>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Urocaridella arabianensis n. sp. Holotype, Female (13 mm): Pereopod I (A); chela of Pereopod I (B); Pereopod II (C); chela of Pereopod II (D); Pereopod III (E); Pereopod IV (F); Pereopod V (G); lateral view of Abdominal pleura (H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954097/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954099>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Urocaridella arabianensis n. sp. Holotype, Female (13 mm): Chela of pereopod III (A); Chela of Pereopod IV (B); Chela of Pereopod V (C); 1st Pleopod (D); Appendix interna (E); Uropod (F); Posterior end of telson (G). Scale bar=0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954099/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954101>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Urocaridella arabianensis n. sp. in live condition (A & B)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954101/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954103>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Biological features of Urocaridella arabianensis n. sp. from Agatti Island, Lakshadweep, India. Size frequency (A); Eggs with eyestalk (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954103/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954105>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. The phylogenetic tree topology for Urocaridella arabianensis n. sp. with congener species based on COI (A), 16S (B) genes sequences using Bayesian inference (BI)/maximum likelihood (ML) analyses." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954107>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. The phylogenetic tree topology for Urocaridella arabianensis n. sp. with congener species based on 18S (A) and H3 (B) genes sequences using Bayesian inference (BI)/maximum likelihood (ML) analyses." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954107/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954109>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Concatenated analysis for the species of Urocaridella arabianensis n. sp. with congener species using Bayesian inference (BI) and maximum likelihood (ML) based on one mitochondrial (16S) and two nuclear gene sequences (H3, 18S)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954109/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

